{"tid":522023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那成都十店舖被換二維碼　顧客電子錢包付款進別人袋","createTime":"2018-01-07T07:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T05:33:35.000Z","uid":60545,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"da7525694ff9f9f2dcd4bbf9d1709c32684c753d","tid":522023,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:16:44.000Z","msg":"內地近年大力推廣使用微信支付等電子平台消費，香港亦愈來愈商戶接受這類電子付款方式，但在方便背後，透過掃瞄二維碼（QR Code）這簡單方式以電子錢包付費，暗藏保安隱憂。成都一條小巷內的10家商舖，就在一夜之間被人偷換付款用的二維碼，顧客付款後金錢轉到同一個人的帳戶，涉事商戶已就事件報警。<br />\n<br />\n事發在成都黨車北站附近一條小巷，發現事件的麵店老闆表示，昨早（1日）約8時，一名食客掃瞄店內微信二維碼付款，他因太忙只匆匆看了對方手機一眼，見顯示成功付款就讓客人離開，無留意自己手機是否收到轉帳。該食客之後到對面另一家店買東西，再透過微信二維碼付款，發現兩店收款人是同一個人，回到麵店告訴老闆揭發事件。<br />\n<br />\n麵店老闆通知周圍的商戶，最終發現共有10家店的二維碼被換，有店主稱客人付款時通知他們，二維碼上「有刀割的痕迹」。亦有店家指每日檢查二維碼，前日（12月31日）都未出問題，估計假冒的二維碼是當晚被換上。<br />\n<br />\n各店家指事件因發現得早，損失最多的一間店失款僅約200元人民幣，已就事件報警。處理案件的派出所指是首次接獲同類案件，但稱透過更換二維碼非法獲利已不是新興作案方式，表明這種行為屬盜竊，又提醒商家每天關店時要收好二維碼，再使用前要先檢查，以免損失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180102/s00004/1514887921703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180102%2Fs00004%2F1514887921703&d=9T5muvOEbKPxekxzFkzEdqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f7eff2b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180102%2Fs00004%2F1514887921703&h=be1b8cf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180102/s00004/1514887921703</a>"},{"pid":"a17ab7d8f67c848346e4f96e5989494d83b3f438","tid":522023,"uid":44105,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"支那宝好先進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c29dc7dc8d5b073286cafb2dd3e8a337bfb2197","tid":522023,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a17ab7d8f67c848346e4f96e5989494d83b3f438","tid":522023,"uid":44105,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"支那宝好先進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:43:27.000Z","msg":"人地怕假銀紙已經好慘喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那宝對於落後兼冇信用保證國家真係好先進嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0aaf6131ce26b28a19feac6f442355f3e5e656","tid":522023,"uid":47359,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:44:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">QR code打手<br />\n1 D wade<br />\n2 姐打羅夫<br />\n3 上坂堇<br />\n4 人生鍾嘉欣<br />\n5 群龍共舞<br />\n6 賈雨村</span>"},{"pid":"a2a1ed2485ba927269fbc1cb12acb7a688d60c0a","tid":522023,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca83890f1712f21f40a860b307433ec666bd4fc","tid":522023,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T08:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2dd164e040a84495dd2a67ce76a314a6c5f9d5c","tid":522023,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6937cdce2265790753823d69d222812e4c23c074","tid":522023,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T11:47:38.000Z","msg":"即刻唸起琴日見到個post話個法國係中國用慣支付寶，返到家鄉無支付寶覺得好落後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係度吹奏支付寶好先進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國班店主係驚收假錢先整個支付寶姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b4194f4feb30b8c60163227021418101a03873","tid":522023,"uid":47359,"lik